 We are seeking enthusiastic, career-minded professionals to join our Sales Team as a Corporate Inside Sales Representative for the Corporate sales segments.
 The ideal Corporate Inside Sales Representative will be aggressive, goal- oriented, articulate and possess sound phone and customer facing skills. A strong personality with the desire to reach high performance goals is a must. In this role, you will work with Acquisition, Development and Retention accounts with primary focus on retention and development growth.
 What You'll Do: 
You will have ownership of a book of accounts; and will have responsibility to exceed revenue, profit and services targets. This position will be responsible for uncovering new opportunities, selling the benefits of the full suite of Lenovo products and services; and selling against the competition. You will work within segment initiatives including weekly forecast and opportunity management.
 The Corporate Inside Sales Representative will also be tightly aligned with Lenovo's strategic business partners and will be expected to drive a significant amount of their revenue growth by leveraging the channel and the various channel incentive programs.
